  "prompt": "Where can I get the solutions of resonance sheets and dpps?",
  "response": "To find solutions for resonance sheets and DPPs (daily practice problems), you can consider the following options:\n\n1. **Official Websites**: Check the official website of the resonance coaching institute or any specific educational platform that provides these materials. They often have resources or forums for students.\n\n2. **Online Forums and Study Groups**: Websites like Quora, Reddit, or specific Facebook groups for students preparing for competitive exams may have shared resources or discussions where you can find solutions.\n\n3. **YouTube Channels**: Many educators and students share solutions to resonance sheets and DPPs on educational YouTube channels. Search for the specific topics or sheet names for relevant videos.\n\n4. **Books and Guides**: Some reference books or guides might include solved problems similar to those found in resonance sheets.\n\n5. **Peer Study Groups**: Collaborating with classmates or joining study groups can be a great way to discuss and solve problems together.\n\n6. **Tutoring Services**: Consider hiring a tutor who is familiar with the resonance materials. They can help explain and work through the problems with you.\n\n7. **Educational Apps**: Some apps or online platforms offer solutions and explanations for a variety of problems in physics, chemistry, and mathematics.\n\nRemember to ensure that any resources you use are legitimate and respect copyright laws.",
